过，见状奋力追击。歹徒持刀反抗，将刘彦腹部、胸部刺伤后逃离现场。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;one-p&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2.2; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot; microsoft=&quot;&quot; segoe=&quot;&quot; hiragino=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; wenquanyi=&quot;&quot; micro=&quot;&quot; font-size:=&quot;&quot; white-space:=&quot;&quot;&gt;　　重庆市监狱管理局微信公号“重庆监狱”11月22日发布消息称，刘彦在与歹徒搏斗中胸部、腹部连中两刀失血过多，伤势严重。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;one-p&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2.2; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot; microsoft=&quot;&quot; segoe=&quot;&quot; hiragino=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; wenquanyi=&quot;&quot; micro=&quot;&quot; font-size:=&quot;&quot; white-space:=&quot;&quot;&gt;　　澎湃新闻了解到，由于刘彦失血过多，他所需的A型血医院欠缺，南川当地网民从朋友圈得知消息后，纷纷到血站献血。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;one-p&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2.2; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot; microsoft=&quot;&quot; segoe=&quot;&quot; hiragino=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; wenquanyi=&quot;&quot; micro=&quot;&quot; font-size:=&quot;&quot; white-space:=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;one-p&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2.2; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot; microsoft=&quot;&quot; segoe=&quot;&quot; hiragino=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; wenquanyi=&quot;&quot; micro=&quot;&quot; font-size:=&quot;&quot; white-space:=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://res.tmlsoft.com/static/Manage/uediter/image/2018/11/24/1543040413612161.png&quot; title=&quot;1543040413612161.png&quot; alt=&quot;1543040413929188.png&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &quot; microsoft=&quot;&quot; segoe=&quot;&quot; hiragino=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; wenquanyi=&quot;&quot; micro=&quot;&quot; font-size:=&quot;&quot; white-space:=&quot;&quot; float:=&quot;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;one-p&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0